usage: maw channel migrate --to-repo [oracle...] [--dry-run] [--remove-global]
  copies global ~/.claude/channels/<oracle>/config.json into
  <repo>/.claude/channel.json so config travels with the repo (#1195).

  no [oracle...] args = migrate every oracle with global config.
  --dry-run            = show what would happen, no writes.
  --remove-global      = delete the global config after a successful copy.
